params.sqlcmd: "select " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" as \\"PROC_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" as \\"CS_PROC_CD\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NAME\\" as \\"PROC_NAME\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" to_char(M_PROC_GRP.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\") as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" to_char(M_PROC_GRP.\\"STANDARD_COST\\") as \\"STANDARD_COST\\", " +" M_PROC_GRP.COMPANY_CD AS \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" SYS_COST_CTRL.ORG_CD AS \\"ORG_CD\\", " +" to_char(M_PROC_GRP.\\"UPDATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS') as \\"UPDATED_DATE\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" as \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\", " +" decode(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\", null, '1', '2') as \\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"SAVE_UPDATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS') as \\"SAVE_UPDATED_DATE\\" " +"from " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF, " +" SYS_COST_CTRL " +"where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\"(+) " +" and M_PROC_GRP.PLANT_CD = SYS_COST_CTRL.PLANT_CD(+) " +"order by " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" ASC, " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_NO\\" DESC"

"insert into " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF(\\"PLANT_CD\\", \\"ITEM_CD\\", \\"CS_PROC_CD\\", \\"RCY_TYP_CD\\", \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\", \\"WS_CD\\", \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", \\"VEND_CD\\", \\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\", \\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\", \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\", \\"COMPANY_CD\\", \\"ORG_CD\\", \\"ONEROUS_CONS_FLG\\", \\"SAVE_UPDATED_DATE\\", \\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\", \\"UPD_FLG\\") " +"values " +" (?, ?, ?, '*', ?, ?, to_number(?), ?, to_number(?), 1, ?, ?, ?, to_number(?), to_date(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS'), to_number(?), 0)"

"select " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" as \\"CS_PROC_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"RCY_TYP_CD\\" as \\"RCY_TYP_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_NAME\\" as \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"WS_CD\\" as \\"WS_CD\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\") as \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"VEND_CD\\" as \\"VEND_CD\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\") as \\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\") as \\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" as \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\") as \\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"COMPANY_CD\\" as \\"COMPANY_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ORG_CD\\" as \\"ORG_CD\\", " +" to_char(T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ONEROUS_CONS_FLG\\") as \\"ONEROUS_CONS_FLG\\" " +"from " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF, " +" M_CS_PROC " +"where " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\"(+) " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"UPD_FLG\\" = 0 " +"order by " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\""

"update " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF " +"set " +" \\"PLANT_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"RCY_TYP_CD\\" = '*', " +" \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"WS_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"VEND_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\" = 1, " +" \\"CLASIFICATION_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ORG_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ONEROUS_CONS_FLG\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"SAVE_UPDATED_DATE\\" = to_date(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS'), " +" \\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"UPD_FLG\\" = 0 " +"where " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF " +"set " +" \\"TRANSACTION_TYP\\" = 3, " +" \\"UPD_FLG\\" = 0 " +"WHERE " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.UPD_FLG = '1' " +" and not exists( " +" select " +" 1 " +" from " +" M_PROC_GRP, " +" M_ITEM " +" where " +" M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\" " +" and M_PROC_GRP.\\"PROC_CD\\" = T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" " +" )"
"select " +" to_char(M_CS_PROC.\\"UPDATE_TYP\\") as \\"UPDATE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" M_CS_PROC " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" M_CS_PROC " +"set " +" \\"CS_PROC_NAME\\" = ?, " +" \\"WS_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"OUTSIDE_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"VEND_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"STD_COST_OF_MONTH\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"STD_COST_UNIT_TYP\\" = to_number(?), " +" \\"UPDATE_TYP\\" = 1, " +" \\"DEL_FLG\\" = 0, " +" \\"COMPANY_CD\\" = ?, " +" \\"ORG_CD\\" = ? " +"where " +" M_CS_PROC.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_CS_PROC.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" as \\"CS_PROC_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"update " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF " +"set " +" \\"UPD_FLG\\" = 1 " +"where " +" T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_ITEM_CS_PROC_IF.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" as \\"CS_PROC_CD\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST " +"where " +" M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM_PROC_COST.\\"CS_PROC_CD\\" <> ?"

"select " +" to_char(nvl(min(ONEROUS_FLG), 0)) AS \\"ONEROUS_FLG\\" " +"from " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST " +"where " +" M_CONS_UNIT_COST.COMPANY_CD = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.PLANT_CD = ? " +" and M_CONS_UNIT_COST.ITEM_CD = ?"
